6. Methodology
Step 1: User Input
• User enters a query in the text box
• Example: "What is BFS?"
Step 2: Query Processing
• Input is converted to lowercase
• Keywords are matched against predefined aliases
Step 3: Algorithm Mapping
{
 "bfs": "Breadth-first search",
 "dfs": "Depth-first search",
 ...
}
Step 4: Wikipedia Fetch
• The mapped topic is searched using Wikipedia API
• Summary is extracted (first 2 lines)
Step 5: Response Display
• Answer is shown in chat format
• Stored in session history
